lead_paragraph: A woman who threw a shoe at Hillary Clinton as the former U.S. secretary of state was delivering a speech in Las Vegas has been released from jail, and faces possible charges after her arrest for disorderly conduct, officials said on Friday.

headline.main: Woman Who Threw Shoe at Hillary Clinton Released From Jail
